{"h4b13996fg12f3g46aagba56ge8fe68e080e6": ["Gone, spoiled meat. Gone from here.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "9f5d76dd-14d5-65b6-4b96-e5f02c38052e"], "hf228bca1g8f35g4c05gb98dg7bd0ac71b9b5": ["Freedom.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "60ea4b1c-0cdb-55ee-d41b-c3cec783897c"], "hcd0dec29g89d2g47feg85a6g7b0fb267c8b2": ["*Skreeee!*", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "e0d7f7ae-121b-de1c-42cf-a5225b394c38"], "h9cdf87b0gcdfdg4182gb9a1g77ec56852ee4": ["*Ssssk.*", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "67ffba9b-1976-7a6c-7ab4-f2c030125e5d"], "hcba72255gcad6g4c5fg93bag1827f03c1cdd": ["*Ssssss.*", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "1e8194d8-f9c9-3d4c-3b1e-e2c7b1a93e8e"], "h46ebb9c5g5c0fg4502g8e8fgc8902f661d93": ["Yes, my desire. Closer, my sweet!", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "457e3504-32cd-fc4a-cff1-4d7a0f03ffa4"], "h0690e5b5g86b0g4862gbe56g0ae89c80694a": ["I will wrap you, and bind you, and bite you, and eat you.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "68d9592d-5c32-48ed-9048-bbd9a792c7c5"], "h3892fffbge097g4ee2gb721gf7370bde9fde": ["You'd get sick if you ate me. I carry a strange curse.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "bc624ff7-8aa5-4510-883e-2e4ee36d033c"], "h5e73cd31g81eag4d2dgbedcg7c0a3cff19b9": ["I see your sickness. A poison in the skull. Do not touch me, do not come close.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "df6f7f1d-45fd-4b7d-e6d7-e495a224d45f"], "h70dda496g542bg45ccga099g737c327069b4": ["I do not get sick. I wrap. I bind. I bite. I eat. ", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "dde0410d-e0c8-a5df-ed9d-f6b0f7cadb2c"], "hb1c6df72g5401g40f3gb2dega4add3f88295": ["You should eat a goblin instead. They're delicious.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "7230322f-92e3-bc31-f2a9-7f2849e3a8bd"], "h9af95ad8gbb96g44eeg9ac4g67d3b0e881c4": ["Delicious - I do not know. But cruel and sharp - yes. Bindable and wrappable and biteable - yes.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "7db6b843-8b4d-b940-40bc-eeaba342ac8a"], "h99eab8e1g0387g43f5gbbfag72198b8d8c2c": ["<i>You </i>must open the door.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "4cc48676-4b7c-bca3-2f27-d6a7258d22a1"], "h206ed677gab8bg472bga492gefb9b70214b7": ["More delicious than you? More bindable? More wrappable? More biteable? No.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "e170923d-f4fb-8a28-aeca-be88dc4e96c4"], "hbe8ea440gcdccg447ag891eg543c49151919": ["*She scuttles toward you, drooling.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "1e68f08b-2869-f429-f70a-72e962ced25e"], "hef230640g0095g4900g884eg093d1c6cd961": ["How dare you. Do you not recognise me? Lolth, Queen of Spiders.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "4b69a14e-8429-c8b3-29df-f9ca2fb4aeaa"], "hbe557467gb3c3g4a08gae69gebe221b1b926": ["Lolth? Is it... you? My queen! My queen of biting. My queen of binding. My queen of wrapping and holding. What would you have me do?", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "70e7f3c4-d8a2-0f3f-49c8-8bc1378146f1"], "hc9105343g2ddbg4b0dgafd0g24e48a813af4": ["Kill the goblins. They displease me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "4ba95f07-474d-66f7-51cb-eb25e67c292d"], "hf2be75b7g26afg4352g9186g6f86817e859b": ["Of course, my queen.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "dd76b4f4-f83b-13f4-fdb2-7d7a32d9c82d"], "h53820b9eged90g4f15g93e2g46bb9874c6c5": ["Open the door so I can do your bidding.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "d76c33b5-004c-c6fc-f23e-8f72b9231b59"], "h4b75dc7fgaac1g4ef1g99a7g41864fe04b2f": ["Their blood will sicken from my bite.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "dedce42e-8d8f-b70d-9e84-fba23167b880"], "hcf60cae8g440dg4287g909cgbc596cdc9bf3": ["Tell me more about this place.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "0b44e24e-2113-2c2c-11e3-8faa20b35908"], "h7d00c932g5929g4358ga7efgdeea3a2271c4": ["There is another drow here, but she has forgotten you, my queen. She is forsaken.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "6ea1b4af-060e-08b9-a8e5-0ccc4e7c160f"], "h0b5cac47gd6f0g4278gb122gf7a17da94a77": ["Stay here. Be still.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "05dc5b96-0ba7-38d6-1ab1-bb9ab652ca61"], "he529ca2egb1d6g4710gac6dgeb7d46c9eb16": ["Yes, my queen.", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "5fc12986-b086-5c62-1672-5b16e43c0578"], "hc6d20552g2ed4g484dgb034g967059a001a2": ["Lolth? Can it be?", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "b5b19ec6-99e9-600e-0e57-3ae12f15cefd"], "h3bc9bdfag1efcg4c67g950dg242a94f19e9d": ["*Suddenly, a suffocating wave of divine rage surges through the spider pit.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "5660d2d5-bd53-df34-3058-990e316d8890"], "hfe2f19f0gb8cbg4315g81e9gbfc0ff67bc15": ["*It hadn't occurred to you that Lolth might be listening.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "14602c72-cc33-8ef6-b294-535fcf5fb0f8"], "h3c69f26fgc37eg4841g9e0bg3560bae1754d": ["*Shaking with the goddess' fury, the spider shrieks, then attacks.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "0defa075-092b-8b1d-e0b3-bd960863dcba"], "hfdc564d9g5fa1g4140ga5dfg2ac4bc351bf1": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "6f07f6bf-da75-c9be-a7b9-0efae155e027"], "ha35b9eecgdaf3g4e35gbe06g34b034a0cb63": ["*The spider seems poised to attack, but she hesitates, tapping her claws as if trying to communicate.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "610ce80b-2dd0-651c-a24a-ff3039092b56"], "hd17726b4g2406g4717g8b9cg4c5a4a5797da": ["*The other spider echoes her.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "c7991204-987a-0986-680f-ed1a741fbffe"], "hf26a453dg10b8g4fe7gace8g12211fb8ba8e": ["<i>Clap your hands together, mimicking her movements.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "8c96dd64-8d03-6358-fa2b-4c10c6657bfd"], "h5ce08999gc61eg4c8cgb420gfe4289e01124": ["*The spider relaxes slightly, but you feel her hunger - and fear - beneath the surface.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "ab8ccf2b-1007-0d6e-eccc-c2f800d0ce31"], "hd0892368g8549g4f97g8659gb64423c0d932": ["<i>Usher her toward the door.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "82188504-f8be-0ba0-a502-9b8229fad55a"], "hf83e08f1gf248g42eegb368g6fa69d2d0b42": ["*She looks to the closed door, drooling.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "36c5fbe6-fbb9-b5b3-60b4-4518e3b67c37"], "h42747c82g9479g4511g9f29g5951d7f66e76": ["*She scuttles toward the door.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "c2e6ecd1-17a3-1b47-df06-46456b83f9c3"], "h6f3bc56cg200dg4b83ga587g38a79c854652": ["*The sound and your movement agitate her. She prepares to strike.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "9661fe44-3ca3-fcad-2c53-9d3872a135ca"], "hd94943f0g7e79g4a24g9c04g4ba44f1418ab": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "2c70d2a2-f1be-0d83-cd8b-1502741e3ca0"], "hf1264277g994eg4c91g8b3agb987dea70864": ["*The spider hisses and attacks.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "c8bb2bd0-23a8-420c-675c-52057a856bf9"], "hdc580dddg69e8g45fbg8055g4cfeb3675e24": ["What would you have me do?", "c3184d85-1e3f-4e64-85bd-5841fef2e27a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "e97ce2c2-09f5-7739-1ba5-e2eb2af8e9bd"], "hf784fadfgb2acg4f45g946bg711a6c88de18": ["Kill the goblins.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "c2d95c4e-dad6-98a0-a476-31e13b76ff56"], "h69e046b5gfa16g4f6bg9345g58a23b108884": ["Stay here for now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_SpiderNest_Spiders.html", "6544ad3f-bb4a-d439-9f1e-794888a73186"]}